code: @Override protected void doExecute(Task task, UpdateCalendarJobAction.Request request, ActionListener<PutCalendarAction.Response> listener) {     Set<String> jobIdsToAdd = Strings.tokenizeByCommaToSet(request.getJobIdsToAddExpression()).     Set<String> jobIdsToRemove = Strings.tokenizeByCommaToSet(request.getJobIdsToRemoveExpression()).     jobResultsProvider.updateCalendar(request.getCalendarId(), jobIdsToAdd, jobIdsToRemove, c -> {         jobManager.updateProcessOnCalendarChanged(c.getJobIds(), ActionListener.wrap(r -> listener.onResponse(new PutCalendarAction.Response(c)), listener::onFailure)).     }, listener::onFailure). }
